,
"text":"Create the block device:\rqemu-img create -f qcow2 /vmdata/working/vm-demo2-disk 5G\r\rAttach the disk image:\rvirsh attach-disk vm-demo2 /vmdata/working/vm-demo2-disk vda --subdriver qcow2 --cache none --persistent\r\rReboot instance\r\rLog into the instance & partition the new device\rfdisk /dev/vda\r'n' - new partition\r'p' - primary partition\r'1' - 1st partition number\r'[default]' - defaults to beginning of the disk\r'[default]' - defaults to end of the disk\r't' - set the type on the partition\r'1' - select 1st partition\r'83' - set to Linux type\r'w' - write changes & exit\r\rFormat the new disk\rmke2fs -j /dev/vda1"}
